properties.Name: BudgetedIncomeStatement
properties.Description:
The budgeted income statement summarized the individual components of revenue and expenses for the budgeting period.

The budget can be divided into quarters or months are appropriate.

Columns.Name: BudgetedIncomeStatementId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Budgeted Income Statement.

Columns.Name: BudgetedIncomeStatementVersionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Budgeted Income Statement Version.

Columns.Name: BudgetedTotalRevenueAmount
Columns.Description: The total budgeted amount of sales and services revenues.

Columns.Name: ActualTotalRevenueAmount
Columns.Description: The actual amount of sales and services revenues.

Columns.Name: BudgetedTotalVariablesExpensesAmount
Columns.Description: The total budgeted variable expenses amount.

Columns.Name: ActualTotalVariablesExpensesAmount
Columns.Description: The actual total variable expenses amount.

Columns.Name: BudgetedTotalFixedExpensesAmount
Columns.Description: The total budgeted amount of fixed expenses.

Columns.Name: ActualTotalFixedExpensesAmount
Columns.Description: The actual total amount of fixed expenses.

Columns.Name: BudgetedNetOperatingIncomeAmount
Columns.Description: The total budgeted net operating income amount.

Columns.Name: ActualNetOperatingIncomeAmount
Columns.Description: The actual net operating income amount.

Columns.Name: BudgetedInterestExpenseAmount
Columns.Description: The total budgeted amount of interest expenses to be subtracted from net operating income = Net Income Before Taxes Amount

Columns.Name: ActualInterestExpenseAmount
Columns.Description: The actual amount of interest expenses to be subtracted from net operating income = Net Income Before Taxes Amount

Columns.Name: BudgetedNetIncomeBeforeTaxesAmount
Columns.Description: The total budgeted net Income before taxes.

Columns.Name: ActualNetIncomeBeforeTaxesAmount
Columns.Description: The actual net Income before taxes.

Columns.Name: BudgetedIncomeTaxesAmount
Columns.Description: The total budgeted income taxes amount due to be applied to Net Income Before Taxes.

Columns.Name: ActualIncomeTaxesAmount
Columns.Description: The actual income taxes amount due to be applied to Net Income Before Taxes.

Columns.Name: BudgetedNetIncomeAmount
Columns.Description: The total budgeted net Income after taxes.

Columns.Name: ActualNetIncomeAmount
Columns.Description: The actual net Income after taxes.

Columns.Name: FinancialBudgetId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Financial Budget.

Columns.Name: FinancialBudgetVersionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Financial Budget Version.
